title: The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt (Patch 1.12.1) (GOG)
description:
Install instructions:
- Run "patch_witcher3_1.10-1.12.1_2.0.0.43.exe"
- Play
PLEASE REMEMBER TO SEED, MANY OTHERS WANT THIS! :)
If you like this game, support the developers and BUY IT!

Change log:
Patch 1.12.1 (21 January 2016)
Hearts of Stone
Fixes a problem whereby boards shown after finishing a game of Gwent were incorrectly grayed out.
Restores the progress bar shown when passing a round during a game of Gwent
